sentence: what are the flight numbers of the flights which go from san francisco to washington via indianapolis
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.flight_number, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"', v5.stop_number FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, flight_stop v5, airport_service v6, city v7 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'SAN FRANCISCO'))) 
AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'WASHINGTON'))) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND ((v5.stop_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'INDIANAPOLIS'))))));
